item.title: Call for speakers and makers
item.description: Looking for speakers for F17 DSI workshops & lightning talks Is your company or department doing something fun and interesting with Data Science? Do you know a coding tip/trick that you would like to share with the community? Do you have some interesting insights that you would like to share? Come share your ideas/thoughts/project/insights with the Data Science community Contact us for more info & to schedule your session.
